| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3133 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 429db32b-038b-5fd7-ab6b-9493f455b3fa"
index=*
